  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "HB 526",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to members of the bar.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 21A to establish parameters for compulsory dues for members of the bar; define who is a member of the bar for purposes of the section; amend KRS 21A.300 and 21A.310 to conform; repeal KRS 21A.160, relating to organization and control of State bar being vested in the Supreme Court.",
